  "text": "Zhu et al. [CITATION_1] noted a positive association between rhinovirus load and each of the following CD 45 + , CD 68 + , and CD 20 + till 4 days after the acute infection. The authors concluded that there is an association between the level of neutrophils and a 10% decrease in FEV 1 .",
